id: pm-web-1qq4
title: Keep pm-web published scoped as @unbrained/pm-web (not unscoped pm-web)
description: "User decision (2026-05-30): pm-web stays published scoped as @unbrained/pm-web. A prior audit agent (commit ae4f607) had flipped package.json name to unscoped pm-web to match the pm- branding convention, but never claimed/published the unscoped name on npm (still E404) — which would have caused publish 404s. @unbrained/pm-web@2026.5.29-1 is already published and working; pm install github.com/unbraind/pm-web is unaffected by the npm scope. Reverted name back to @unbrained/pm-web. This is the one intentional scope exception in the otherwise-unscoped pm- ecosystem."
type: Decision
status: closed
priority: 2
tags: []
created_at: "2026-05-30T21:48:03.737Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-30T21:48:14.110Z"
author: codex
close_reason: Closed via pm update
